{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270100/extras/\u7c7b\u578b\u4e3b\u9898.png?t=1607921940\" /><br>A strategy game designed based on ancient books such as &quot;Sun Tzu's Art of War&quot; and &quot;Six Tao&quot;. The background is set in the Warring States Period<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270100/extras/\u5386\u53f2\u6218\u5f79.png?t=1607921940\" /><br>Battles such as &quot;Chang Ping&quot;, &quot;Yi Que&quot; and &quot;Yan Ying&quot; designed based on real history.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270100/extras/\u6218\u672f\u5173\u5361.png?t=1607921940\" /><br>Can play &quot;Robbery Grain Road&quot;, &quot;Robbed Camp Village&quot;, &quot;Segmented Encirclement&quot; and &quot;Suspicious Soldier&quot;.<br>There are currently 22 levels.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270100/extras/\u540e\u52e4\u5730\u7406.png?t=1607921940\" /><br>In order to show the role of &quot;logistics,&quot; the actual topography of China was restored as much as possible.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270100/extras/\u5175\u79cd\u7f16\u5236.png?t=1607921940\" /><br>It is no longer an extremely simplified design such as &quot;Cavalry to defeat infantry and infantry to defeat archers&quot;.<br>At present, there are 7 types of arms &quot;WuCai&quot;, &quot;Wing Car&quot;, &quot;Wuqi&quot;, &quot;Ruiqi&quot;, &quot;Wuzu&quot;, &quot;Chongsi&quot; and &quot;Ruishi&quot;.<br>And there are concepts such as &quot;weave&quot;, &quot;front&quot; and &quot;morale strike&quot;.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270100/extras/\u5c06\u9886\u80fd\u529b.png?t=1607921940\" /><br>It is no longer a heroic, simpler design like &quot;force, intelligence, physical strength&quot;.<br>At present, there are 20 generals' capabilities such as &quot;snap formation, combat gear, Shang Yangliang, ears and eyes, Fa-rectification, and general food&quot;.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u884c\u5175\u5fa1\u654c","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/afabce976b8c46516983f621c2913738ab66af40.jpg"},{"name":"\u56db\u4e94\u590d\u4e4b","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/13ef431d1d0f62376926f805a773c666c1f928e0.jpg"},{"name":"\u5341\u5219\u56f4\u4e4b","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/5009daa0d55ad650f6b2c3ba92e40d8a6f635858.jpg"},{"name":"\u8d1f\u5d4e\u4f9d\u9669","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/16842d7b54850959e04685548af88286ffec9ddd.jpg"},{"name":"\u4e58\u5954\u9010\u5317","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/5b02cde4013a424b9354b504ced54e7870e0ea15.jpg"},{"name":"\u7f2e\u7532\u5389\u5175","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/73a1b7af846d98746c230ec576c9c9e5ddfd4141.jpg"},{"name":"\u517b\u5175\u5343\u65e5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/c59f5c67f39b75714d36c2e0f820f90fc84e1245.jpg"},{"name":"\u5b89\u8425\u624e\u5be8","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/20f65b28ab93f17f591f2ffed70931ede268247c.jpg"},{"name":"\u4e07\u7bad\u9f50\u53d1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/41c45c8affe3bc088f1de552b8b784edc5e8cd54.jpg"},{"name":"\u62e9\u5730\u800c\u6218","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1270100/b1f65b05e9bf0bca5461fb8dc66f149d1c5bd45a.jpg"}],"total":26}